{"tid":31005,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新聞通識　1500元　用完即棄　無後座力　肩上反坦克炮","createTime":"2016-12-09T12:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T16:22:10.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cac8623619bb9b77f540aaaaea06ca99979786ce","tid":31005,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8pn4CH3R4v8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8pn4CH3R4v8&d=H%2BmGSSDlm%2F1MMi2VZFfN638C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=71c25057\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8pn4CH3R4v8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美軍將向伊拉克軍提供一批肩托式無後座力炮，協助抵禦伊斯蘭國武裝分子。這款無後座力炮令一般步兵都有可能威脅裝甲車等目標，而且成本低，用完即棄，是有效及方便的武器。 <br />\n<br />\nAT4 的可靠之處是不需要臨場組裝，只需一個步兵加一個肩膊，就足以令敵方戰車報銷。它是一種肩托式無後座力炮，通常用來攻擊裝甲車或坦克，有效射程達三百米，由瑞典在八十年代開發，後來亦被美軍採用。在一九九一年波斯灣戰爭也有上陣。 <br />\n<br />\nAT4 的特色之一是用完即棄。在出廠的時候，發射筒已預先裝好。一發炮彈，瞄準後，一按掣就發射。之後發射筒可以即場捨棄，對步兵來說相當方便。而且發射筒連炮彈每枝價格只是一千五百美元，被視有效對付軍車和防禦工事的低價武器。但對於現代主戰坦克則未必有足夠殺傷力。 <br />\n<br />\nAT4 之所以易用另一原因是它沒有後座力。原理是發射的瞬間，後方會噴出氣體抵消反作用力，但同時會爆出一下後噴火焰。所以使用者在發射前，必須轉頭確定後面沒有自己人，亦令 AT4 只能在空曠環境發射。但後來出現的改良版 AT4-CS 就解決這限制。做法是用鹽水中和後噴火焰，令 AT4 可以在室內向外發射，但代價就是降低破壞力。 <br />\n<br />\n坊間有不少文章都誤會 AT4 是「火箭筒」。但其實 AT4 發射的不是火箭彈，而是普通炮彈。靠炮筒加速提供初始動力，但離開炮筒後，只靠慣性飛行。火箭彈則有自己的動力裝置，所以 AT4 只是無後座力炮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/rXFOvj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FrXFOvj&h=9e613c79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/bdhI0x\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FbdhI0x&h=84bbab1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/5OvP8E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F5OvP8E&h=179d26d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/JywIho\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FJywIho&h=0e17a851&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b3b5a1b4c1c41bf14faec716736ab20673bb7ec","tid":31005,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:07:03.000Z","msg":"淘寶幾時有得賣"},{"pid":"e9b757df60d619c344bd82e0626d8c6e24debe67","tid":31005,"uid":26922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:08:30.000Z","msg":"無後座力炮，好似番左去CoH 咁，101傘兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7439b951b1f5bdb75b54b9639b19a139c52002b","tid":31005,"uid":34705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:22:02.000Z","msg":"一皮嘢左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66cb3e50e1aa303f709282e1f5169ea2abb1045","tid":31005,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:48:43.000Z","msg":"又送嘢俾isis<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f227dc4ae611f4f98c57644d9b95237506d57e","tid":31005,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:05:06.000Z","msg":"AT4唔係咩新野，而且好多坦克裝甲已經頂得到AT4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70b8b4fb8c8ee3a2d009b9d4455534d10707f42","tid":31005,"uid":13556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:27:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>AT4唔係咩新野，而且好多坦克裝甲已經頂得到AT4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港d警車頂唔頂到"},{"pid":"af2a6c646e340e66090c488a1d24cb0eb5105e24","tid":31005,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>AT4唔係咩新野，而且好多坦克裝甲已經頂得到AT4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港d警車頂唔頂到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"5197b9671be1b9c3d2a2ede196f726eae441ec7a","tid":31005,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無後座力炮，好似番左去CoH 咁，101傘兵<img src=\"/asset